game.name: Tom & Jerry : Mouse Maze
game.description:
Tom & Jerry: Mouse Maze is a brand new arcade game that is inspired by the most recognized kids cartoon show. The entire screen is full of cheese and you have to help your most favorite Jerry to get them all. This job is not easy at all since Tom is on the prowl. He has chosen you to get him through all the hurdles. We hope you will join this fun puzzle game to assist him in the race through fun-packed levels! Make sure to keep him away from the cat in this one of the coolest and classic games for cat and mouse!ï¿½
You have five modes: School, First Floor, Bedroom, Cellar and Attic to explore. In each mode, you will have 10 levels to play. Guide Jerry to his hole once he finishes all the cheese that you see on the screen of your game! Try to create a short path so that he can accomplish his job in the shortest time possible since it is a time-based game! Remember you can only move to the advanced level if you have cleared the previous level. Try to complete each level with 3 Stars to earn the maximum possible points!
In the second level of the school mode, you will have to avoid the traps and clean the oil spots. Jerry will be lost while meeting with the wrong thing. However, you will also have an option to revive him if this happens. You will only 1 free revive in this level of this cute fun puzzle. Guiding him to reach the hole after getting all the cheese you see will help you clear the level and move to the advanced stage! Try to collect at least 20 stars in each level and complete all levels in the previous version to access to the next mode! Play more HTML5 games on our free online game website!
